@startuml
' Diagram: F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app (Sequence)
' Status: VERIFIED
' Baseline: branch master, current worktree @ HEAD 0121e4f
' Source:
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml.cs: OnGetAsync(), OnGetPendingSnapshotAsync(), OnPostApproveAsync(), OnPostRejectAsync()
' - VinhKhanhTour.CMS/Pages/DuyetThanhToan/Index.cshtml: polling PendingSnapshot
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/YeuCauThanhToan.cs
' - VinhKhanhTour.API/Models/DangKyApp.cs
' Note: Sequence khop voi PageModel hien tai, gom snapshot polling, approve, reject, va redirect theo tab.
' Note: Sequence chi mo ta handler/PageModel/AppDbContext/PostgreSQL o cap hanh vi; khong liet ke cau SQL.
title F08 - Duyet hoac tu choi thanh toan goi app

actor Admin
boundary "DuyetThanhToan.cshtml JS" as JS
control "DuyetThanhToan IndexModel" as IndexModel
participant "AppDbContext\n<<persistence>>" as DbContext
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

Admin -> IndexModel: OnGetAsync(tab)
IndexModel -> DbContext: YeuCauThanhToans.AsNoTracking().ToListAsync()
DbContext -> DB: read payment request rows
DB --> DbContext: rows
DbContext --> IndexModel: danh sach
IndexModel --> Admin: render request table

loop JS polling snapshot
  JS -> IndexModel: OnGetPendingSnapshotAsync()
  IndexModel -> DbContext: YeuCauThanhToans.CountAsync()/FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read pending snapshot
  DB --> DbContext: count + latest row
  DbContext --> IndexModel: count + latest
  IndexModel --> JS: JSON Count, LatestId, LatestTransferContent
end

alt admin duyet
  Admin -> IndexModel: OnPostApproveAsync(yeuCauId)
  IndexModel -> DbContext: YeuCauThanhToans.FirstOrDefaultAsync()\nDangKyApps.FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read request and current subscription rows
  DB --> DbContext: rows
  DbContext --> IndexModel: data
  note right of IndexModel
    OnPostApproveAsync() computes
    mocBatDau and NgayHetHan.
  end note
  IndexModel -> DbContext: SaveChangesAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: persist approval result
  DB --> DbContext: saved
  IndexModel --> Admin: Redirect ?tab=cho_duyet
else admin tu choi
  Admin -> IndexModel: OnPostRejectAsync(yeuCauId, lyDo)
  IndexModel -> DbContext: YeuCauThanhToans.FirstOrDefaultAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: read target request row
  DB --> DbContext: request row
  DbContext --> IndexModel: request
  IndexModel -> DbContext: SaveChangesAsync()
  DbContext -> DB: persist reject result
  DB --> DbContext: saved
  IndexModel --> Admin: Redirect ?tab=tu_choi
end
@enduml
